{"tid":2337150,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"aespa《Black Mamba》MV抄襲爭議！SM：「我們聯繫被提及的作者、公司等，確認MV場景無異議」","createTime":"2020-12-23T06:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T07:59:33.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7002da40d1f998d4cf764e7089e041de8aa69545","tid":2337150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"SM新女團「aespa」上個月帶著《Black Mamba》正式出道，MV也引發抄襲爭議。<br />\n<br />\n許多場景會讓人聯想到《英雄聯盟》虛擬女團K/DA的《POP/STARS》，德國視覺藝術家Vacades（Timo Helgert）通過IG發文：「我收到很多訊息，他們沒有經過我的同意，我們也沒有合作，看上去像是抄襲（地鐵、蛇這兩個場景）。」該藝術家隔幾天後也發文：「我和aespa的MV導演已經溝通過了，雙方都能理解對方的創作過程。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_88b9566f56a775d154ca7f30cd89b444/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-22/132507-890082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_88b9566f56a775d154ca7f30cd89b444%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-22%2F132507-890082.jpg&h=2ed0e27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_215533538eaf69e0f22f96baea1f98c2/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-22/132507-890083.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_215533538eaf69e0f22f96baea1f98c2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-22%2F132507-890083.jpg&h=9f54fe76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這也在網路引發熱烈討論，網友：「SM每次都出現抄襲爭議才匯款嗎」、「如果原作者什麼都不做會怎樣呢」等等，並要求SM娛樂發表的立場。（相關新聞：aespa的MV抄襲爭議，被抄襲藝術家回應：已經溝通過了！網友：「SM每次都出現爭議才要匯款嗎」）<br />\n<br />\n事情經過快一個月後，SM娛樂在22日發表了立場：「與被提及《Black Mamba》像似部分相關作者、公司等取得聯繫，說明了企劃意圖、世界觀，並進行了交談。相關作者、公司等了解本公司的企劃和製作過程，並確認MV畫面無異議。」"},{"pid":"73f4540424f4fae263edd819cf59465ed0c60dbd","tid":2337150,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"Sm做嘢唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02f4277825948f9668455c50589b6f4af21b7f2","tid":2337150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73f4540424f4fae263edd819cf59465ed0c60dbd","tid":2337150,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"Sm做嘢唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"Don't be cocky<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e0538828074e3e6d240bf139d9811df4309d23","tid":2337150,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"完蛋了....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0015e526b70d21db50e662aef88e6878c6cccc","tid":2337150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5e0538828074e3e6d240bf139d9811df4309d23","tid":2337150,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"完蛋了....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:09:39.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520f15f576aa4581291b8d98801abfdf01016894","tid":2337150,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b02f4277825948f9668455c50589b6f4af21b7f2","tid":2337150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73f4540424f4fae263edd819cf59465ed0c60dbd","tid":2337150,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"Sm做嘢唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"Don't be cocky<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p